  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the iron-teppan vessel to 350\u000045.",
    "Saut\u00192 the onion and garlic in olive oil until softened.",
    "Add the cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper, and stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add the baked beans, red kidney beans, and water to the vessel, and stir to combine.",
    "Cover the vessel with a lid, and bake for 30 minutes.",
    "Reduce the heat to 200\u000045, and continue baking for an additional 60 minutes, or until the beans are tender and the liquid has reduced.",
    "Let the stew rest for 10 minutes before serving."
